                            <comment id="32715" author="jcl" created="Thu, 29 Mar 2012 04:02:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;After landing of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-787&quot; title=&quot;ftruncate blocks when done holding a group lock&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-787&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-787&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; I have updated the patch to change only sanity.sh to:&lt;/p&gt;
